{"tid":1535382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"顏色水處理方法","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:29:24.000Z","uid":45502,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa7c5f40831ac87933129b2899294d19dbb08bf","tid":1535382,"uid":45502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"去五金搵acetone (亞士通）<br />\n$20/L ,有效溶解acrylic 同所有有機顏料同膠水，包括螢光粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要係水洗唔甩嘅嘢佢都洗得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢洗唔甩唔該用水洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申chem JJ,冇見過佢同水洗唔甩嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc2ede6ab097c9533eefea18f6b01943310c56c","tid":1535382,"uid":45502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"92defb652c9401518bbb70a2d4dbb503878228e8","tid":1535382,"uid":45502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"5f17b501159d9a851d1954d497ff8e95697b04be","tid":1535382,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30109968c27fc7f829c68f1033ebd48080385258","tid":1535382,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"67a3e6de596f78c57d276b8be178e515381871fc","tid":1535382,"uid":45502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:09.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"15ccac19f3d65692c82b0e8ee46b7df1161120d0","tid":1535382,"uid":36927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"啲亞士通好撚毒嫁"},{"pid":"0dc478224dcddb0c49178ff34bf7b3dc13af5865","tid":1535382,"uid":45502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"066a9ff55a940a8c03def15f049aa2cfeb7875a3","tid":1535382,"uid":45502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"964934c88637d04feabb05232cd31175f079b70a","tid":1535382,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:43